<br />\n<br />\n  夢見雞飛的宜忌：<br />\n<br />\n  「宜」宜泡腳，宜吃醋，宜追問真相。<br />\n<br />\n  「忌」忌喝碳酸飲料，忌坐檯階上曬太陽，忌逛眼鏡店。"},{"pid":"8bddbdeaedf00cfe3e2cf59b80168f708c45b85c","tid":2228930,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:30:46.000Z","msg":"政府比左幾百億<br />\n都要炒人"},{"pid":"69b072c9edca98bcddfa3f733da115feac79c962","tid":2228930,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f598eb8f5a9a51f6c54031009a0792fccd7ec5","tid":2228930,"uid":3113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:50:53.000Z","msg":"召喚空姐Betty<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"Betty真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356f45151df791d9969be02b9730d7278bf6de02","tid":2228930,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"有冇消息？"},{"pid":"367e3a496574ec53fee0c8e177549f75956939f3","tid":2228930,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6086b3bbe3faee9dc833b5556872b16a9d5d7bf2","tid":2228930,"uid":366993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xiYiXn2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxiYiXn2.jpg&h=762fc9b7&s={SIZE}\" /> 早知當年做地產，可能唔駛好似宜家咁下海<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/749523795057716/posts/4436415109701881/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F749523795057716%2Fposts%2F4436415109701881%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=204c9b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/749523795057716/posts/4436415109701881/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:01:40.000Z","msg":"咁平嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /